        "subject": "LU-14055 all: Enable debugfs macros fallback to PDE_DATA",
        "message": "LU-14055 all: Enable debugfs macros fallback to PDE_DATA\n\nThe existing procfs macros fallback to using PDE_DATA when\ninode i_private is NULL.\nWhen switching to debugfs macros this fallback needs to be\ncontinued\n\nFixes: 76626d6c52 (\"LU-13344 all: Separate debugfs and procfs handling\")\nSigned-off-by: Shaun Tancheff <shaun.tancheff@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I90333b53539dcc166170ba121d1c176c6f818930\n"
